	(TclpCreateProcess):
	* mac/tclMacFile.c (TclpGetCwd):
	* generic/tclEncoding.c (Tcl_GetDefaultEncodingDir)
	(Tcl_SetDefaultEncodingDir,Tcl_GetEncodingName)
