2002-01-07  Don Porter <dgp@users.sourceforge.net>

	* generic/tclEvent.c (TclInExit):
	* generic/tclIOUtil.c (SetFsPathFromAbsoluteNormalized,
	(SetFsPathFromAny,Tcl_FSNewNativePath,DupFsPathInternalRep):
